&lt;p&gt;&quot;flume-ng avro-client --conf ../conf/ -H 0.0.0.0 -p 41415 -F ~/.bash_profile -R timestamp=389908323&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13258100" author="inder" created="Fri, 20 Apr 2012 09:06:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Updated the client to read headers from a property file.&lt;br/&gt;
Sample header.properties&lt;br/&gt;
------------------------------------&lt;br/&gt;
streamName = sample-stream&lt;br/&gt;
timestamp=2189128912&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Client command line looks like -&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; ./flume-ng avro-client --conf ../conf/ -H localhost -p 41414 -F ~/.bash_profile -R headers.properties&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
